t;fix&quot; hot water when all we had to do was turn switch on. But were never told to turn switch on. Never alerted to switch altogether. Still, the hotel itself was fine, we loved it. Loved the on-site restaurant, delicious food, lovely service. Loved (LOVED) the pool scene, adored the location adjacent to Dubai Mall. Would stay at Address again in a heartbeat -- though we would insist on room in the hotel portion and we'd make time for more than just one night.And p.s. the water light shows in the lake between the Address and the Burj Dubai, oh, my, so magical. The whole experience -- just too short!	
